sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Admin as Admin
    participant FE as Admin Portal<br/>Next.js :3001
    participant BE as Backend<br/>Express API
    participant DB as Database<br/>PostgreSQL
    participant Discord as Discord<br/>Bot Service
    participant Notif as Notifikasi<br/>Email dan N8N

    Admin ->> FE: Buka /admin/tickets<br/>Klik Input Tiket Support
    activate FE
    FE -->> Admin: Tampil Form Input Tiket Support
    deactivate FE

    Admin ->> FE: Isi form - Nama, Email, Divisi,<br/>Jenis Support, Deskripsi
    activate FE
    FE ->> FE: Validasi semua field
    Admin ->> FE: Klik Submit
    FE ->> BE: POST /api/tickets/create (type=SUPPORT)
    deactivate FE
    activate BE

    BE ->> BE: Ticket Service - createTicket
    BE ->> BE: Classifier - classifyTicketFields
    Note over BE: Hasil: category, priority, keywords

    BE ->> DB: ticket.create (form_id=admin_portal)
    activate DB
    DB -->> BE: ticket id dan ticketNumber
    deactivate DB

    BE ->> DB: activity.create (TICKET_CREATED, admin_manual)

    par Notifikasi Paralel
        BE ->> Discord: postNewTicketEmbed (ticket)
        activate Discord
        Discord -->> BE: threadId
        deactivate Discord
    and
        BE ->> Notif: sendConfirmation (pemohon.email)
        activate Notif
        Notif -->> BE: Email terkirim
        deactivate Notif
    and
        BE ->> Notif: triggerWorkflow (ticket.created)
        activate Notif
        Notif -->> BE: N8N triggered
        deactivate Notif
    end

    BE -->> FE: 201 Created - ticketId, ticketNumber
    deactivate BE
    FE -->> Admin: Redirect /admin/tickets/id + sukses